rd of Brightwater Keep\">Lord of Brightwater Keep</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\">Maesters</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Magic\" title=\"Magic\">Magic</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Magpie\" title=\"Magpie\">Magpie</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Nightfire\" title=\"Nightfire\">Nightfire</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Poison\" title=\"Poison\">Poison</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Queen%27s_men\" title=\"Queen&#39;s men\">Queen's men</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">R'hllor</a> (Lord of Light)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rainbow_Guard\" title=\"Rainbow Guard\">Rainbow Guard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Raven\" title=\"Raven\">Raven</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Redwyne_fleet\" title=\"Redwyne fleet\">Redwyne fleet</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Renly%27s_peach\" title=\"Renly&#39;s peach\">Renly's peach</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Royal_fleet\" title=\"Royal fleet\">Royal fleet</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">Septon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">Smallfolk</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Smuggling\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Smuggling\">Smuggling</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Turncloak\" title=\"Turncloak\">Turncloak</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_42&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-wid